content.name: Remove Fog: Home of Light
content.description: Fog in Cold Star [CS], Home of Light [HL] and Toride [TO] becomes invisible. Should improve FPS.
content.author: Vectorial1024

text.name: 去去雾气走：Home of Light
text.description: [CS]、[HL]及[TO]的雾气不再可见。应可提升帧率(FPS)。

text.name: 去去霧氣走：Home of Light
text.description: [CS]、[HL]及[TO]的霧氣不再可見。應可提升幀率(FPS)。
